{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Evidently, I-- I didn't give her any reason to don't do this or don't do that, because I was an obedient child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't think that she said, don't do this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't ever a question of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the talk that I--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was cold in the cars, in these--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--cattle cars that you were in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they had slats, which had two-inch separations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was two buckets, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we didn't have enough water, enough food, so the use of it was-- it was not constantly used, but there was still-- eventually, it was still very foul smelling.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we were getting dirtier and the-- the cars were not cleaned before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so whatever was there-- the use of it was made before, it was on our clothings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a very, very hard time to live in those cars for that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I don't know how many days it took.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember her face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came with the-- with the dogs, the German shepherds, and the whips.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the direct light came right at you, shone right at you with a very, very bright light.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would have not done this in the daytime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a feeling the daytime would have been less scary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the night, the darkness, the bright lights, the dogs the-- the yelping and the whipping of the whips and the screaming-- and-- and they didn't want anyone to be emotional.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just didn't let you hug long enough or-- And my mother went to one side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I remember her eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
